" vi macros for latex
"
" itemize (command mode)
:map ;it a\begin{itemize}\end{itemize}ko  \item
" itemize (insert mode)
:map! ;it \begin{itemize}\end{itemize}ko  \item
" emphasize word in command mode
:map ;em i{\em lewa}
" emphasize word in insert mode
:map! ;em bi{\em lea}
